{"tid":1610110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非係時候幫手，係屋企都可以為前線做準備","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T16:13:49.000Z","uid":161011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e094dea490ebfe7c3fe07d4016818658f96d74ff","tid":1610110,"uid":161011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"你哋唔上場，但都可以幫手，就係儲雞蛋殼，但請改改開雞蛋方法，盡量開口細啲，用水簡單沖一沖唔會發臭，畀前線好好運用，可以的話，入啲膠水又好、黑漆又好、咩都得啦，跟著用膠紙封口，或用熱溶膠封口又得。<br />\n<br />\n有隻膠水建議，就係用來痴膠地板嗰啲咖啡色膠水，一百蚊一大桶，粘度高難清理，旺角廣東道一帶賣膠地板舖頭有售。"},{"pid":"d2f799f99b8457509e946739fa8775daa659a7dd","tid":1610110,"uid":122972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:39:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7637e898ebc78fe26095221b9a1980ccd2eda7b7","tid":1610110,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">示威者對藍絲商鋪係「針對性打擊」，唔係「破壞」</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad319a1878030d177c02d918722fde28e211751","tid":1610110,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"銀髮軍師 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非</span>加入 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戰況大增千倍</span>的新戰術<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613583</a>"}]}